    		</span>
    	</div>
    	<div class="linegroup">
    		<span class="operItem">
	    		<!--<label class="required">*</label>-->
				<label class="name">器械护士一</label>
				<input class="value" id="ScrubNurFirst" key="" type="keyvalue" style="width:150px;"></input>
				<a class="button" href="#" id="btScrubNurFirst">…</a>
